import Tile from './Tile'
import '../styling/BoardRow.css'

const BoardRow = (props) => {
    return (
        <tr className='row'>
            <Tile coords={props.ids[0]} />
            <Tile coords={props.ids[1]} />
            <Tile coords={props.ids[2]} />
            <Tile coords={props.ids[3]} />
            <Tile coords={props.ids[4]} />
            <Tile coords={props.ids[5]} />
        </tr>
    )
}

export default BoardRow
